# Welcome to Keywords Extractor ğŸ£
This is a simple library for extracting keywords from a text. It is based on the [TF-IDF](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tf%E2%80%93idf) algorithm for extracting keywords. Beside, it also uses the [YAKE](https://github.com/LIAAD/yake) and [RapidFuzz](https://github.com/maxbachmann/RapidFuzz) libraries.

Fast and easy to use. But it still works better than the other libraries I've tried. I think so  (â—Â´Ï‰ï½€â—).

If you have any complain, my mail here  (>â€˜oâ€™)>: trinhhungsss492@gmail.com. Or my facebook here  (ï½¡â—•â€¿â—•ï½¡): https://www.facebook.com/trinhdoduyhungss.


## Installation
Download and install through pip with wheel support:
```bash
pip install kwextractor
```
## Usage
```python
from kwextractor.process.extract_keywords import ExtractKeywords
from kwextractor.process.extract_numverse import ExtractNumverse
from kwextractor.process.replacing_w2n import ReplacingWtoN
keywords = ExtractKeywords().extract_keywords("tÃ´i thÃ­ch nghe cÃ¡c báº£n nháº¡c cá»§a Trá»‹nh CÃ´ng SÆ¡n")
print(keywords) # "báº£n nháº¡c,Trá»‹nh CÃ´ng SÆ¡n"
num_verse = ExtractNumverse().extract_numverse("sinh cho tui bÃ i thÆ¡ gá»“m hai chá»¥c cÃ¢u nhÃ©",20) #20 is the maximum value returned. It can be any integer number, you can set it fit your need.
print(num_verse) # 20
replacing_w2n = ReplacingWtoN().replacing_w2n("cho há»i lÃ m sao Ä‘á»ƒ sinh ra mÆ°á»i bÃ i thÆ¡")
print(replacing_w2n) # "cho há»i lÃ m sao Ä‘á»ƒ sinh ra 10 bÃ i thÆ¡"
keywords = ExtractKeywords().extract_keywords("Tá»•ng thá»‘ng Má»¹ Donald Trump Ä‘Ã£ Ä‘á» nghá»‹ cÃ¡c nÆ°á»›c thÃ nh viÃªn NATO tÄƒng cÆ°á»ng Ä‘áº§u tÆ° trong lÄ©nh vá»±c an ninh, Ä‘áº·c biá»‡t lÃ  trong lÄ©nh vá»±c phÃ²ng chá»‘ng táº¥n cÃ´ng tá»« cÃ¡c quá»‘c gia cÃ³ thá»ƒ xÃ¢m nháº­p vÃ o cÃ¡c thÃ nh phá»‘ cá»§a cÃ¡c nÆ°á»›c thÃ nh viÃªn. ÄÃ¢y lÃ  láº§n Ä‘áº§u tiÃªn tá»•ng thá»‘ng Má»¹ Ä‘á» nghá»‹ cÃ¡c nÆ°á»›c thÃ nh viÃªn NATO tÄƒng cÆ°á»ng Ä‘áº§u tÆ° trong lÄ©nh vá»±c an ninh.")
print(keywords) # "cÆ°á»ng Ä‘áº§u,quá»‘c gia,xÃ¢m nháº­p,ninh Ä‘áº·c,an ninh,Donald Trump,Tá»•ng thá»‘ng lÄ©nh vá»±c phÃ²ng chá»‘ng táº¥n cÃ´ng,NATO"
```

